OL,4,BWatford: Nigel Pearson succeeds Quique
OL,5,BSanchez Flores as manager
OL,6, Watford have appointed Nigel Pearson as
OL,7, manager until the end of the season.
OL,9,FThe former Leicester City boss will
OL,10,Ftake charge after Saturday's Premier
OL,11,FLeague match against Crystal Palace.
OL,13,FThe 56-year-old is Watford's third
OL,14,Fmanager of the season following Quique
OL,15,FSanchez Flores' sacking on Sunday after
OL,16,Fless than 90 days in charge.
OL,18,F"Nigel comes with all of the experience
OL,19,Fand success we believe can have a very
OL,20,Fpositive impact on our season,"
OL,21,Fchairman Scott Duxbury said.
